BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 254.16 750 Td (WHAT IS DBT?) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 0.5 w 72 738 m 540 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 710 Td (Dialectical Behavior Therapy \(DBT\) was developed by Dr. Marsha Linehan.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 692 Td (It combines cognitive-behavioral techniques with mindfulness practices.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 674 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 656 Td (DBT teaches four core skill sets:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 638 Td (  1. MINDFULNESS - Being present and aware without judgment) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 620 Td (  2. DISTRESS TOLERANCE - Surviving crisis without making it worse) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 602 Td (  3. EMOTION REGULATION - Understanding and managing emotions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 584 Td (  4. INTERPERSONAL EFFECTIVENESS - Getting needs met in relationships) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 566 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 548 Td (The Dialectic: Two things can be true at the same time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 530 Td (  - I am doing my best AND I can do better.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 512 Td (  - I can accept myself AND want to change.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 494 Td (  - This is painful AND I can cope with it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 476 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 458 Td (How to use this workbook:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 440 Td (  - Work through each module in order or as directed by your therapist) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 422 Td (  - Practice skills daily, not just during crisis) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 404 Td (  - Use the diary cards to track your progress) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 386 Td (  - Be patient with yourself - skills take time to master) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
